    "description": {
      "value": "<p> As part of the requirements of this jutsu, you must have the Double Headed Wolf Inuzuka clan jutsu active. <br />You perform a much more devastating variation of the tunneling fang as a double headed wolf, tearing into your target and ripping them apart. <br />Make a melee Taijutsu attack, dealing 5d6 slashing &amp; 5d6 piercing damage. </p><p><br />At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 2d6 for each damage type.</p>",
